com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube

Interface DupleCubeAggregator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CubeAggregator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CountDistinctCubeAggregator, DefaultDupleCubeAggregator, EasyCubeAggregatorBridge

    public interface DupleCubeAggregator
extends CubeAggregator
    Interface that specifies aggregators for the CUBE operator that can rollup inner dimensions.

    Specifically, this aggregator applies for the cases where the grain of the data is greater as the grain of the CUBE. In other words, there are "inner dimensions" that need to be rolled up before computing the cube.

    This interface extends the CubeAggregator interface, and specified one extra method:

    • innerAggregate: aggregate values for inner dimension for the specified value cuboid.
